软件包 org.biosino.CHS.ontology

类摘要
Chromosome This class describes the chromosomes.
CHS This class describe a chromosomal homology segment(CHS), which contains a pair of GenoLocs .
Gene This class descending from GenoLoc describes a gene.
GenoLoc This class descending from Chromosome describes a location in a genome.
